{"tid":2287812,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[借朋友AC] 我家狗狗其實而家係有咩病?","createTime":"2020-11-16T05:06:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T05:40:02.000Z","uid":16562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"529e6aeaffa2ef1e28ffe0603c629cad1b026028","tid":2287812,"uid":16562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T05:06:36.000Z","msg":"我想借朋友AC開post的 因為好緊急而我呢邊而家夜晚，想出左post問下大家點睇先，我聽日點都會帶佢睇醫生了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n是咁的 我家老人家 最近其中一隻腳仔（大脾腳背咁上下位腫左有血包），仲會自己脹到自動爆血，試過放完血過一排都腫番，所以帶左佢去睇獸醫，獸醫同佢驗左血話整體都正常，仲開左啲十日抗生素同一枝消炎藥膏比佢，係呢十日入面係睇得出明顯消左腫仲好番左既，果枝藥膏個獸醫話搽完又唔洗cum住佢 結果基本上枝藥膏hi晒地同佢會自己lam番, 所以搽左幾日就冇搽。<br />\n<br />\n但問題來了，食完十日既抗生素，而家又復發，到底點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪關啲藥膏冇搽足定咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我上網睇過如果係癌，好似唔會腫都唔會有血水自己爆出黎，列底咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d5b848a810da381c80bcac624bdf2253e474e2","tid":2287812,"uid":109670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T05:31:18.000Z","msg":"睇第二個"},{"pid":"ebc9cce8767d0d17b3441af075cbde472c776bc5","tid":2287812,"uid":109670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T05:31:31.000Z","msg":"sorry 推返"},{"pid":"643c4e9485e32cff7991d3ff24b5e0963dbd4fe2","tid":2287812,"uid":16562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebc9cce8767d0d17b3441af075cbde472c776bc5","tid":2287812,"uid":109670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T05:31:31.000Z","msg":"sorry 推返"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-